        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#robinson1913"/>, p. 162, n. <citedRange>12</citedRange></bibl>, and 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#marengo1991a"/>, pp. <citedRange>490-491, footnote 1</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>41.1690</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>009420</citedRange></bibl>
                    <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, pp. <citedRange>171-174</citedRange> (date, content), p. <citedRange>308</citedRange>, number 50 (text)</bibl>.</p>
                    <p>For a general bibliography on accounts of damiergoi see at <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr011400</ref>.</p>                
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
